data.description: Solid Bones of a BLOCK home with NO HOA! All your big ticket items are taken care of - NEW Trane AC, Roof, Water Heater. GRAND LOT of 11,408 sqft, is a perfect blank slate for your dream landscaping! Home sits on a wide CUSTOM street, near Westgate, Cardinals Stadium, Casino, Park, Frwy, & upcoming main attraction of Glendale, the VAI Resort... this one is a STEAL! 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, & 2 large living rooms which has enough space to add a 4th bedroom. Upgrades include Kitchen Cabinets, Granite Countertops, Stainless Steel Appliances, New Master Bathroom Vanity, & New Toilets. Other perks include a Walk-In Master Closet, Fireplace in step down living room, Extended Covered Back Patio with block fence, & 2 car garage with an extra tandem space!  All it needs is your personal touch!
